                            <comment id="384270" author="adilger" created="Wed, 30 Aug 2023 19:27:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It would be useful to include entries for some of the remaining xattrs:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;user.job&lt;/tt&gt; holds jobid name that initially created the file (from &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13031&quot; title=&quot;store JobID of program that created file in inodes at create time&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-13031&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-13031&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;trusted.dmv&lt;/tt&gt; holds default directory layout inherited by new subdirectories&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;filter.fid&lt;/tt&gt; on OST objects and holds back-pointer to MDT FID that contains object and layout information specific to that object&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
